<H1>YOU'RE REALLY INTO IT NOW!!!</H1>
Cards Left: <%= @play_deck.size %><br>  
<BR>
Dealer's Hand: <% @dealer_hand.each do |x| %><%= "#{x} | " %><% end %> Total: <%= @dealer_total %><BR>
User's Hand: <% @user_hand.each do |x| %><%= "#{x} | " %><% end %> Total: <%= @user_total %><BR>
